Introduction

varPro is a CRAN compliant R-package implementing variable priority [1] in a variety of problems. The package uses fast OpenMP parallel processing to construct forests for regression, classification, survival analysis and unsupervised problems. The package is constantly being worked on and many new kinds of applications, forests and tree constructions will be added to it in the near future.
